            {
               "text": "### Images from Biblioteca Nacional Digital\n\nThese images are copyright for Biblioteca Nacional Digital and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
