            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 1</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"bndPortugal6r\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('bndPortugal6r', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Sheet of the Treaty of Tordesillas (<htcite0>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Family: Lem/Leme - An analysis of the history of this family, which participated in landmark events such as the Treaty of Tordesillas and the Paulista Civil War (<htcite1>).</li><li>Indigenous Peoples of São Vicente, Brazil (Pindorama) (<htdate0> - <hdate1>): Indigenous peoples who lived in the captaincy of São Vicente in the first centuries of the colonization of Brazil (*Pindorama*) (<htcite2>).</li><li>Sources: Text explaining which sources are used in research and in History Traces (<htcite3>).</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
